        "content": "## Watcher — Teams transcripts → inbox\nEvery 15 min: read the watchlist (allow-listed people) → pull each person's meeting transcripts in the last 35 min → dedupe by transcript id → drop into `inbox` (pending) → fire the Main Pipeline once per NEW call.\n\n**Edge case handled:** 2 calls → 2 inbox rows → 2 pipeline runs, each claims its own row (FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED). Transcripts never mix.",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 420
      },
