        "content": "## ⚠️ Before going live — confirm 3 things\n1. **Credential 'MS Graph'** — Entra app with `OnlineMeetingTranscript.Read.All` (application) + an application access policy granting it. Select it on the 3 HTTP nodes.\n2. **Endpoints** — if your original working automation used different Graph URLs/params, paste it and I'll drop them in exactly.\n3. **Watchlist** — run `db/2026-07_watchlist.sql` and insert the real GUIDs/UPNs.\n\nThen pick the target workflow on 'Trigger pipeline'.",
        "height": 300,
